Require Import UniMath.CategoryTheory.Core.Categories.
Require Import UniMath.CategoryTheory.Core.Isos.
Require Import UniMath.CategoryTheory.Core.Functors.
Require Import UniMath.CategoryTheory.Core.NaturalTransformations.
Require Import UniMath.CategoryTheory.PrecategoryBinProduct.

Local Open Scope cat.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Definition of prebicategory                                                     *)
(*                                                                                     *)
(** *** Data                                                                           *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Definition prebicat_2cell_struct (C : precategory_ob_mor)
  : UU
  := ‚àè (a b: C), C‚ü¶a, b‚üß ‚Üí C‚ü¶a, b‚üß ‚Üí UU.

Definition prebicat_1_id_comp_cells : UU
  := ‚àë (C : precategory_data), prebicat_2cell_struct C.

Coercion precat_data_from_prebicat_1_id_comp_cells (C : prebicat_1_id_comp_cells)
  : precategory_data
  := pr1 C.

Definition prebicat_cells (C : prebicat_1_id_comp_cells) {a b : C} (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : UU
  := pr2 C a b f g.

Local Notation "f '==>' g" := (prebicat_cells _ f g) (at level 60).
Local Notation "f '<==' g" := (prebicat_cells _ g f) (at level 60, only parsing).

Definition prebicat_2_id_comp_struct (C : prebicat_1_id_comp_cells) : UU
  :=
       (* 2-unit *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), f ==> f)
     √ó (* left unitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), identity _ ¬∑ f ==> f)
     √ó (* right unitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), f ¬∑ identity _  ==> f)
     √ó (* left inverse unitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), identity _ ¬∑ f <== f)
     √ó (* right inverse unitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), f ¬∑ identity _  <== f)
     √ó (* right associator *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : C‚ü¶c, d‚üß),
        (f ¬∑ g) ¬∑ h ==> f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h))
     √ó (* left associator *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : C‚ü¶c, d‚üß),
        f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h) ==> (f ¬∑ g) ¬∑ h)
     √ó (* vertical composition *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g h : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), f ==> g -> g ==> h -> f ==> h)
     √ó (* left whiskering *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g1 g2 : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß),
        g1 ==> g2 ‚Üí f ¬∑ g1 ==> f ¬∑ g2)
     √ó (* right whiskering *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f1 f2 : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß),
        f1 ==> f2 ‚Üí f1 ¬∑ g ==> f2 ¬∑ g).

Definition prebicat_data : UU := ‚àë C, prebicat_2_id_comp_struct C.

Definition make_prebicat_data C (str : prebicat_2_id_comp_struct C)
  : prebicat_data
  := C,, str.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** Data projections.                                                                  *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Coercion prebicat_cells_1_id_comp_from_prebicat_data (C : prebicat_data)
  : prebicat_1_id_comp_cells
  := pr1 C.

Definition id2 {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) : f ==> f
  := pr1 (pr2 C) a b f.

Definition lunitor {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : identity _ ¬∑ f ==> f
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 C)) a b f.

Definition runitor {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : f ¬∑ identity _ ==> f
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))) a b f.

Definition linvunitor {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : identity _ ¬∑ f <== f
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))) a b f.

Definition rinvunitor {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : f ¬∑ identity _ <== f
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))) a b f.

Definition rassociator {C : prebicat_data} {a b c d : C}
           (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : C‚ü¶c, d‚üß)
  : (f ¬∑ g) ¬∑ h ==> f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h)
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))) a b c d f g h.

Definition lassociator {C : prebicat_data} {a b c d : C}
           (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : C‚ü¶c, d‚üß)
  : f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h) ==> (f ¬∑ g) ¬∑ h
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))) a b c d f g h.

Definition vcomp2 {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} {f g h: C‚ü¶a, b‚üß}
  : f ==> g ‚Üí g ==> h ‚Üí f ==> h
  := Œª x y, pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))) _ _ _ _ _ x y.

Definition lwhisker {C : prebicat_data} {a b c : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) {g1 g2 : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
  : g1 ==> g2 ‚Üí f ¬∑ g1 ==> f ¬∑ g2
  := Œª x, pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))) _ _ _ _ _ _ x.

Definition rwhisker {C : prebicat_data} {a b c : C} {f1 f2 : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
  : f1 ==> f2 ‚Üí f1 ¬∑ g ==> f2 ¬∑ g
  := Œª x, pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))) _ _ _ _ _ _ x.

Local Notation "x ‚Ä¢ y" := (vcomp2 x y) (at level 60).
Local Notation "f ‚óÉ x" := (lwhisker f x) (at level 60). (* \tw *)
Local Notation "y ‚ñπ g" := (rwhisker g y) (at level 60). (* \tw nr 2 *)

Definition hcomp {C : prebicat_data} {a b c : C} {f1 f2 : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} {g1 g2 : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
  : f1 ==> f2 -> g1 ==> g2 -> f1 ¬∑ g1 ==> f2 ¬∑ g2
  := Œª x y, (x ‚ñπ g1) ‚Ä¢ (f2 ‚óÉ y).

Definition hcomp' {C : prebicat_data} {a b c : C} {f1 f2 : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} {g1 g2 : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
  : f1 ==> f2 -> g1 ==> g2 -> f1 ¬∑ g1 ==> f2 ¬∑ g2
  := Œª x y, (f1 ‚óÉ y) ‚Ä¢ (x ‚ñπ g2).

Local Notation "x ‚ãÜ y" := (hcomp x y) (at level 50, left associativity).

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Laws                                                                            *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** The numbers in the following laws refer to the list of axioms given in ncatlab
    (Section "Definition / Details")
    https://ncatlab.org/nlab/show/bicategory#detailedDefn
    version of October 7, 2015 10:35:36                                                *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Definition prebicat_laws (C : prebicat_data)
  : UU
  :=   (** 1a id2_left *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g), id2 f ‚Ä¢ x = x)
     √ó (** 1b id2_right *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g), x ‚Ä¢ id2 g = x)
     √ó (** 2 vassocr *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g h k : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g) (y : g ==> h) (z : h ==> k),
        x ‚Ä¢ (y ‚Ä¢ z) = (x ‚Ä¢ y) ‚Ä¢ z)
     √ó (** 3a lwhisker_id2 *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß), f ‚óÉ id2 g = id2 _)
     √ó (** 3b id2_rwhisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß), id2 f ‚ñπ g = id2 _)
     √ó (** 4 lwhisker_vcomp *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g h i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (x : g ==> h) (y : h ==> i),
        (f ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ (f ‚óÉ y) = f ‚óÉ (x ‚Ä¢ y))
     √ó (** 5 rwhisker_vcomp *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f g h : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (x : f ==> g) (y : g ==> h),
        (x ‚ñπ i) ‚Ä¢ (y ‚ñπ i) = (x ‚Ä¢ y) ‚ñπ i)
     √ó (** 6  vcomp_lunitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g),
        (identity _ ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ lunitor g = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x)
     √ó (** 7 vcomp_runitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g),
        (x ‚ñπ identity _) ‚Ä¢ runitor g = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x)
     √ó (** 8 lwhisker_lwhisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h i : c --> d) (x : h ==> i),
        f ‚óÉ (g ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (f ¬∑ g ‚óÉ x))
     √ó (** 9 rwhisker_lwhisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g h : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (i : c --> d) (x : g ==> h),
        (f ‚óÉ (x ‚ñπ i)) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ ((f ‚óÉ x) ‚ñπ i))
     √ó (** 10 rwhisker_rwhisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (h : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (i : c --> d) (x : f ==> g),
        lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ ((x ‚ñπ h) ‚ñπ i) = (x ‚ñπ h ¬∑ i) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _)
     √ó (** 11 vcomp_whisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (h i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (x : f ==> g) (y : h ==> i),
        (x ‚ñπ h) ‚Ä¢ (g ‚óÉ y) = (f ‚óÉ y) ‚Ä¢ (x ‚ñπ i))
     √ó (** 12a lunitor_linvunitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), lunitor f ‚Ä¢ linvunitor _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 12b linvunitor_lunitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), linvunitor f ‚Ä¢ lunitor _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 13a runitor_rinvunitor *)
       (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), runitor f ‚Ä¢ rinvunitor _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 13b rinvunitor_runitor *)
     (‚àè (a b : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß), rinvunitor f ‚Ä¢ runitor _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 14a lassociator_rassociator *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d),
        lassociator f g h ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 14b rassociator_lassociator *)
       (‚àè (a b c d : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d),
        rassociator f g h ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = id2 _)
     √ó (** 15 runitor_rwhisker *)
       (‚àè (a b c : C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß),
        lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (runitor f ‚ñπ g) = f ‚óÉ lunitor g)
     √ó (** 16  lassociator_lassociator *)
       (‚àè (a b c d e: C) (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d) (i : C‚ü¶d, e‚üß),
        (f ‚óÉ lassociator g h i) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _  ‚Ä¢ (lassociator _ _ _ ‚ñπ i) =
        lassociator f g _  ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _).


B: prebicat_data
H: ‚àè (a b : B) (f g : B ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß), isaset (f ==> g)
isaprop (prebicat_laws B)


B: prebicat_data
H: ‚àè (a b : B) (f g : B ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß), isaset (f ==> g)
isaprop (prebicat_laws B)

  repeat (apply isapropdirprod)
  ; repeat (apply impred ; intro)
  ; apply H.
Qed.

Definition prebicat : UU := ‚àë C : prebicat_data, prebicat_laws C.

Coercion prebicat_data_from_bicat (C : prebicat) : prebicat_data := pr1 C.
Coercion prebicat_laws_from_bicat (C : prebicat) : prebicat_laws C := pr2 C.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** Laws projections.                                                                  *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Section prebicat_law_projections.

Context {C : prebicat}.

(** 1a id2_left *)
Definition id2_left {a b : C} {f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} (x : f ==> g)
  : id2 f ‚Ä¢ x = x
  := pr1 (pr2 C) _ _ _ _ x.

(** 1b id2_right *)
Definition id2_right {a b : C} {f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} (x : f ==> g)
  : x ‚Ä¢ id2 g = x
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 C)) _ _ _ _ x.

(** 2 vassocr *)
Definition vassocr {a b : C} {f g h k : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß}
           (x : f ==> g) (y : g ==> h) (z : h ==> k)
  : x ‚Ä¢ (y ‚Ä¢ z) = (x ‚Ä¢ y) ‚Ä¢ z
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))) _ _ _ _ _ _ x y z.

(** 3a lwhisker_id2 *)
Definition lwhisker_id2 {a b c : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
  : f ‚óÉ id2 g = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))) _ _ _ f g.

(** 3b id2_rwhisker *)
Definition id2_rwhisker {a b c : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
  : id2 f ‚ñπ g = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))) _ _ _ f g.

(** 4 lwhisker_vcomp *)
Definition lwhisker_vcomp {a b c : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) {g h i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
           (x : g ==> h) (y : h ==> i)
  : (f ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ (f ‚óÉ y) = f ‚óÉ (x ‚Ä¢ y)
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))) _ _ _ f _ _ _ x y.

(** 5 rwhisker_vcomp *)
Definition rwhisker_vcomp {a b c : C} {f g h : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß}
           (i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (x : f ==> g) (y : g ==> h)
  : (x ‚ñπ i) ‚Ä¢ (y ‚ñπ i) = (x ‚Ä¢ y) ‚ñπ i
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))) _ _ _ _ _ _ i x y.

(** 6  vcomp_lunitor *)
Definition vcomp_lunitor {a b : C} (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g)
  : (identity _ ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ lunitor g = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))) _ _ f g x.

(** 7 vcomp_runitor *)
Definition vcomp_runitor {a b : C} (f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (x : f ==> g)
  : (x ‚ñπ identity _) ‚Ä¢ runitor g = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))) _ _ f g x.

(** 8 lwhisker_lwhisker *)
Definition lwhisker_lwhisker {a b c d : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
           {h i : c --> d} (x : h ==> i)
  : f ‚óÉ (g ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (f ¬∑ g ‚óÉ x)
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))) _ _ _ _ f g _ _ x.

(** 9 rwhisker_lwhisker *)
Definition rwhisker_lwhisker {a b c d : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) {g h : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
           (i : c --> d) (x : g ==> h)
  : (f ‚óÉ (x ‚ñπ i)) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ ((f ‚óÉ x) ‚ñπ i)
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))))) _ _ _ _ f _ _ i x.

(** 10 rwhisker_rwhisker *)
Definition rwhisker_rwhisker {a b c d : C} {f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} (h : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
           (i : c --> d) (x : f ==> g)
  : lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ ((x ‚ñπ h) ‚ñπ i) = (x ‚ñπ h ¬∑ i) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))) _ _ _ _ _ _ h i x.

(** 11 vcomp_whisker *)
Definition vcomp_whisker {a b c : C} {f g : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß} {h i : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß}
           (x : f ==> g) (y : h ==> i)
  : (x ‚ñπ h) ‚Ä¢ (g ‚óÉ y) = (f ‚óÉ y) ‚Ä¢ (x ‚ñπ i)
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))))))) _ _ _ _ _ _ _ x y.

(** 12a lunitor_linvunitor *)
Definition lunitor_linvunitor {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : lunitor f ‚Ä¢ linvunitor _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))))) _ _ f.

(** 12b linvunitor_lunitor *)
Definition linvunitor_lunitor {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : linvunitor f ‚Ä¢ lunitor _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))))))))) _ _ f.

(** 13a runitor_rinvunitor *)
Definition runitor_rinvunitor {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : runitor f ‚Ä¢ rinvunitor _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))))))) _ _ f.

(** 13b rinvunitor_runitor *)
Definition rinvunitor_runitor {a b : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß)
  : rinvunitor f ‚Ä¢ runitor _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))))))))))) _ _ f.

(** 14a lassociator_rassociator *)
Definition lassociator_rassociator {a b c d : C}
           (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d)
  : lassociator f g h ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))))))))) _ _ _ _ f g h.

(** 14b rassociator_lassociator *)
Definition rassociator_lassociator {a b c d : C}
           (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d)
  : rassociator f g h ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _ = id2 _
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C))))))))))))))))))) _ _ _ _ f g h.

(** 15 runitor_rwhisker *)
Definition runitor_rwhisker {a b c : C} (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß)
  : lassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (runitor f ‚ñπ g) = f ‚óÉ lunitor g
  := pr1 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
      (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))))))))))) _ _ _ f g .

(** 16  lassociator_lassociator *)
Definition lassociator_lassociator {a b c d e: C}
           (f : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß) (g : C‚ü¶b, c‚üß) (h : c --> d) (i : C‚ü¶d, e‚üß)
  : (f ‚óÉ lassociator g h i) ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _  ‚Ä¢ (lassociator _ _ _ ‚ñπ i) =
    lassociator f g _  ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
  := pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2
       (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 (pr2 C)))))))))))))))))))) _ _ _ _ _ f g h i.

End prebicat_law_projections.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Bicategories                                                                    *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Definition isaset_cells (C : prebicat) : UU
  := ‚àè (a b : C) (f g : a --> b), isaset (f ==> g).

Definition bicat : UU
  := ‚àë C : prebicat, isaset_cells C.

Definition build_bicategory
           (C : prebicat_data)
           (HC1 : prebicat_laws C)
           (HC2 : isaset_cells (tpair _ C HC1))
  : bicat
  := tpair _ (tpair _ C HC1) HC2.


ob: UU
mor: ob ‚Üí ob ‚Üí UU
cell: ‚àè X Y : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor X Y ‚Üí UU
id‚ÇÅ: ‚àè X : ob, mor X X
comp: ‚àè X Y Z : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor Y Z ‚Üí mor X Z
id‚ÇÇ: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y), cell X Y f f
vcomp: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f g h : mor X Y),
cell X Y f g ‚Üí cell X Y g h ‚Üí cell X Y f h
lwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (f : mor X Y) 
(g h : mor Y Z),
cell Y Z g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z f g) (comp X Y Z f h)
rwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (g h : mor X Y) 
(f : mor Y Z),
cell X Y g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z g f) (comp X Y Z h f)
lunitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f) f
lunitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f)
runitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y)) f
runitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y))
lassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
  (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
rassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
  (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))

cell X Y (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y)) f
runitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y))
lassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
  (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
rassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
  (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
‚àè (a b c d : ob) (f : mor a b) 
(g : mor b c) (h : mor c d),
cell a d (f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h) (f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h))

‚àè (a b : ob) (f g h : mor a b),
cell a b f g ‚Üí cell a b g h ‚Üí cell a b f h
 exact vcomp.
      
ob: UU
mor: ob ‚Üí ob ‚Üí UU
cell: ‚àè X Y : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor X Y ‚Üí UU
id‚ÇÅ: ‚àè X : ob, mor X X
comp: ‚àè X Y Z : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor Y Z ‚Üí mor X Z
id‚ÇÇ: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y), cell X Y f f
vcomp: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f g h : mor X Y),
cell X Y f g ‚Üí cell X Y g h ‚Üí cell X Y f h
lwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (f : mor X Y) 
(g h : mor Y Z),
cell Y Z g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z f g) (comp X Y Z f h)
rwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (g h : mor X Y) 
(f : mor Y Z),
cell X Y g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z g f) (comp X Y Z h f)
lunitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f) f
lunitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f)
runitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y)) f
runitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y))
lassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
  (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
rassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
  (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
‚àè (a b c : ob) (f : mor a b) (g1 g2 : mor b c),
cell b c g1 g2 ‚Üí cell a c (f ¬∑ g1) (f ¬∑ g2)
 exact lwhisk.
      
ob: UU
mor: ob ‚Üí ob ‚Üí UU
cell: ‚àè X Y : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor X Y ‚Üí UU
id‚ÇÅ: ‚àè X : ob, mor X X
comp: ‚àè X Y Z : ob, mor X Y ‚Üí mor Y Z ‚Üí mor X Z
id‚ÇÇ: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y), cell X Y f f
vcomp: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f g h : mor X Y),
cell X Y f g ‚Üí cell X Y g h ‚Üí cell X Y f h
lwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (f : mor X Y) 
(g h : mor Y Z),
cell Y Z g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z f g) (comp X Y Z f h)
rwhisk: ‚àè (X Y Z : ob) (g h : mor X Y) 
(f : mor Y Z),
cell X Y g h
‚Üí cell X Z (comp X Y Z g f) (comp X Y Z h f)
lunitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f) f
lunitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X X Y (id‚ÇÅ X) f)
runitor: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y)) f
runitor_inv: ‚àè (X Y : ob) (f : mor X Y),
cell X Y f (comp X Y Y f (id‚ÇÅ Y))
lassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
  (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
rassocor: ‚àè (W X Y Z : ob) (f : mor W X)
(g : mor X Y) (h : mor Y Z),
cell W Z (comp W Y Z (comp W X Y f g) h)
  (comp W X Z f (comp X Y Z g h))
‚àè (a b c : ob) (f1 f2 : mor a b) (g : mor b c),
cell a b f1 f2 ‚Üí cell a c (f1 ¬∑ g) (f2 ¬∑ g)
 exact rwhisk.
Defined.

Coercion prebicat_of_bicat (C : bicat)
  : prebicat
  := pr1 C.

Definition cellset_property {C : bicat} {a b : C} (f g : a --> b)
  : isaset (f ==> g)
  := pr2 C a b f g.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Invertible 2-cells                                                              *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Definition is_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
           {a b : C} {f g : a --> b} (Œ∑ : f ==> g)
  : UU
  := ‚àë œÜ : g ==> f, Œ∑ ‚Ä¢ œÜ = id2 f √ó œÜ ‚Ä¢ Œ∑ = id2 g.

Definition make_is_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
           {a b : C} {f g : a --> b}
           {Œ∑ : f ==> g}
           {œÜ : g ==> f}
           (Œ∑œÜ : Œ∑ ‚Ä¢ œÜ = id2 f)
           (œÜŒ∑ : œÜ ‚Ä¢ Œ∑ = id2 g)
  : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑
  := œÜ,, make_dirprod Œ∑œÜ œÜŒ∑.

Definition inv_cell {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} {f g : a --> b} {Œ∑ : f ==> g}
  : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑ ‚Üí g ==> f
  := pr1.

(* TODO: Reorganize notations. *)
Declare Scope bicategory_scope.
Notation "inv_Œ∑ ^-1" := (inv_cell inv_Œ∑) : bicategory_scope.
Delimit Scope bicategory_scope with bicategory.
Bind Scope bicategory_scope with bicat.
Local Open Scope bicategory_scope.

Definition vcomp_rinv {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} {f g : a --> b}
           {Œ∑ : f ==> g} (inv_Œ∑ : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑)
  : Œ∑ ‚Ä¢ inv_Œ∑^-1 = id2 f
  := pr1 (pr2 inv_Œ∑).

Definition vcomp_linv {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} {f g : a --> b}
           {Œ∑ : f ==> g} (inv_Œ∑ : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑)
  : inv_Œ∑^-1 ‚Ä¢ Œ∑ = id2 g
  := pr2 (pr2 inv_Œ∑).

Definition is_invertible_2cell_inv {C : prebicat_data} {a b : C} {f g : a --> b}
           {Œ∑ : f ==> g} (inv_Œ∑ : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑)
  : is_invertible_2cell (inv_Œ∑^-1)
  := make_is_invertible_2cell (vcomp_linv inv_Œ∑) (vcomp_rinv inv_Œ∑).

Definition is_invertible_2cell_id‚ÇÇ {C : prebicat} {a b : C} (f : a --> b)
  : is_invertible_2cell (id2 f)
  := make_is_invertible_2cell (id2_left (id2 f)) (id2_left (id2 f)).

y, z: g ==> h
R: x ‚Ä¢ y = x ‚Ä¢ z
inv_x ^-1 ‚Ä¢ (x ‚Ä¢ y) = z

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß

inv_x: is_invertible_2cell x
h: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
y, z: g ==> h
R: x ‚Ä¢ y = x ‚Ä¢ z
y = inv_x ^-1 ‚Ä¢ (x ‚Ä¢ y)

h: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
y, z: g ==> h
R: x ‚Ä¢ y = x ‚Ä¢ z
y = id2 g ‚Ä¢ y
 apply (!id2_left _).
  
C: prebicat

h: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß

 apply id2_left.
Qed.


C: bicat

  apply (!vcomp_rinv _).

(* ------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(* Locally groupoidal                                                        *)
(* ------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
Definition locally_groupoid
           (B : bicat)
  : UU
  := ‚àè (x y : B)
       (f g : x --> y)
       (Œ± : f ==> g),
     is_invertible_2cell Œ±.


B: bicat
isaprop (locally_groupoid B)


B: bicat
isaprop (locally_groupoid B)

  
B: bicat
t, t0: B
t1, t2: B ‚ü¶ t, t0 ‚üß
t3: t1 ==> t2
isofhlevel 1 (is_invertible_2cell t3)

  apply isaprop_is_invertible_2cell.
Qed.

(* ------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(* invertible_2cell                                                          *)
(* ------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Definition invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
           {a b : C} (f g : a --> b) : UU
  := ‚àë Œ∑ : f ==> g, is_invertible_2cell Œ∑.

Definition make_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
         {a b : C} {f g : C‚ü¶a,b‚üß}
         {Œ∑ : f ==> g} (inv_Œ∑ : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑)
  : invertible_2cell f g
  := Œ∑,, inv_Œ∑.

Coercion cell_from_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
         {a b : C} {f g : a --> b} (Œ∑ : invertible_2cell f g)
  : f ==> g
  := pr1 Œ∑.

Coercion property_from_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat_data}
         {a b : C} {f g : a --> b}
         (Œ∑ : invertible_2cell f g)
  : is_invertible_2cell Œ∑
  := pr2 Œ∑.

Definition id2_invertible_2cell {C : prebicat} {a b : C} (f : a --> b)
  : invertible_2cell f f
  := make_invertible_2cell (is_invertible_2cell_id‚ÇÇ f).


C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
x = y


C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
x = y

  
C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
x = y

  
C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
isPredicate is_invertible_2cell
C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
pr1 x = pr1 y

  
C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
isPredicate is_invertible_2cell
 
C: bicat

f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x, y: invertible_2cell f g
p: x = y
x0: f ==> g
isaprop (is_invertible_2cell x0)
 apply isPredicate_is_invertible_2cell.
  
C: bicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß

p: x = y
pr1 x = pr1 y
 apply p.
Defined.

(** ** Derived laws                                                                    *)

Definition vassocl {a b : C} {f g h k : C‚ü¶a, b‚üß}
           (x : f ==> g) (y : g ==> h) (z : h ==> k)
  : (x ‚Ä¢ y) ‚Ä¢ z = x ‚Ä¢ (y ‚Ä¢ z)
  := !vassocr x y z.

rassociator f (identity b) g ‚Ä¢ (f ‚óÉ lunitor g) =
runitor f ‚ñπ g

  apply lunitor_lwhisker.
Qed.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Interchange law                                                                 *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)


C: prebicat
a, b, c: C
f1, g1, h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2, g2, h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2
(x1 ‚Ä¢ y1) ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚Ä¢ y2) = x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚Ä¢ y1 ‚ãÜ y2


C: prebicat
a, b, c: C
f1, g1, h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2, g2, h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2
(x1 ‚Ä¢ y1) ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚Ä¢ y2) = x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚Ä¢ y1 ‚ãÜ y2

  
C: prebicat
a, b, c: C
f1, g1, h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2, g2, h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2
(x1 ‚Ä¢ y1) ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚Ä¢ y2) =
((x1 ‚ñπ f2) ‚Ä¢ (g1 ‚óÉ x2)) ‚Ä¢ ((y1 ‚ñπ g2) ‚Ä¢ (h1 ‚óÉ y2))

  
C: prebicat
a, b, c: C
f1, g1, h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2, g2, h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2
(x1 ‚Ä¢ y1) ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚Ä¢ y2) =
(((x1 ‚ñπ f2) ‚Ä¢ (g1 ‚óÉ x2)) ‚Ä¢ (y1 ‚ñπ g2)) ‚Ä¢ (h1 ‚óÉ y2)

  
C: prebicat
a, b, c: C
f1, g1, h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2, g2, h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2

(** ** Homs are categories                                                             *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Section Hom_Spaces.

Context {C : prebicat} (a b : C).

Definition hom_ob_mor
  : precategory_ob_mor
  := make_precategory_ob_mor (C‚ü¶a,b‚üß) (Œª (f g : C‚ü¶a,b‚üß), f ==> g).

Definition hom_data
  : precategory_data
  := make_precategory_data hom_ob_mor id2 (Œª f g h x y, x ‚Ä¢ y).


C: prebicat
a, b: C
is_precategory hom_data


C: prebicat
a, b: C
is_precategory hom_data

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
is_precategory_one_assoc hom_data

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0), id2 a0 ‚Ä¢ f = f
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0), f ‚Ä¢ id2 b0 = f
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 c d : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0)
(g : b0 ==> c) (h : c ==> d),
f ‚Ä¢ (g ‚Ä¢ h) = (f ‚Ä¢ g) ‚Ä¢ h

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0), id2 a0 ‚Ä¢ f = f
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
‚àè f0 : f ==> g, id2 f ‚Ä¢ f0 = f0
 apply id2_left.
  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0), f ‚Ä¢ id2 b0 = f
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
‚àè f0 : f ==> g, f0 ‚Ä¢ id2 g = f0
 apply id2_right.
  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
‚àè (a0 b0 c d : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß) (f : a0 ==> b0)
(g : b0 ==> c) (h : c ==> d),
f ‚Ä¢ (g ‚Ä¢ h) = (f ‚Ä¢ g) ‚Ä¢ h
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g, h, i: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
‚àè (f0 : f ==> g) (g0 : g ==> h) (h0 : h ==> i),
f0 ‚Ä¢ (g0 ‚Ä¢ h0) = (f0 ‚Ä¢ g0) ‚Ä¢ h0
 apply vassocr.
Qed.

Definition hom_precategory
  : precategory
  := make_precategory hom_data is_precategory_hom.

End Hom_Spaces.


C: bicat
a, b: C
has_homsets (hom_data a b)


C: bicat
a, b: C
has_homsets (hom_data a b)

  exact (@cellset_property C a b).
Qed.

Definition hom {C : bicat} (a b : C) : category
  := hom_precategory a b ,, @cellset_property C a b.

(** ** Functor structure on horizontal composition.                                    *)

Section hcomp_functor.

Context {C : bicat} {a b c : C}.

functor_data (category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c))
  (hom a c)


C: bicat

functor_data (category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c))
  (hom a c)

‚àè a0 b0 : category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c),
category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c) ‚ü¶ a0, b0 ‚üß
‚Üí hom a c ‚ü¶ pr1 a0 ¬∑ pr2 a0, pr1 b0 ¬∑ pr2 b0 ‚üß

  
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
‚àè a0 b0 : category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c),
category_binproduct (hom a b) (hom b c) ‚ü¶ a0, b0 ‚üß
‚Üí hom a c ‚ü¶ pr1 a0 ¬∑ pr2 a0, pr1 b0 ¬∑ pr2 b0 ‚üß
 
C: bicat

‚àè a0 b0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß,
precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
  (hom_ob_mor b c) a0 b0
‚Üí pr1 a0 ¬∑ pr2 a0 ==> pr1 b0 ¬∑ pr2 b0
 
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
  (hom_ob_mor b c) (f1,, f2) (g1,, g2)
‚Üí pr1 (f1,, f2) ¬∑ pr2 (f1,, f2) ==>
  pr1 (g1,, g2) ¬∑ pr2 (g1,, g2)

  
C: bicat

f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
hom_ob_mor a b ‚ü¶ pr1 (f1,, f2), pr1 (g1,, g2) ‚üß
√ó hom_ob_mor b c ‚ü¶ pr2 (f1,, f2), pr2 (g1,, g2) ‚üß
‚Üí pr1 (f1,, f2) ¬∑ pr2 (f1,, f2) ==>
  pr1 (g1,, g2) ¬∑ pr2 (g1,, g2)
 
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f1 ==> g1 √ó f2 ==> g2 ‚Üí f1 ¬∑ f2 ==> g1 ¬∑ g2

  
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
x: f1 ==> g1
y: f2 ==> g2
f1 ¬∑ f2 ==> g1 ¬∑ g2
 apply hcomp; assumption.
Defined.


C: bicat
a, b, c: C
is_functor hcomp_functor_data


C: bicat
a, b, c: C
is_functor hcomp_functor_data

  
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
‚àè a0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß,
id2 (pr1 a0) ‚ãÜ id2 (pr2 a0) = id2 (pr1 a0 ¬∑ pr2 a0)
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
‚àè (a0 b0 c0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
(f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) a0 b0)
(g : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) b0 c0),
(pr1 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g) ‚ãÜ (pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr2 g) =
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g ‚ãÜ pr2 g

  
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
‚àè a0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß,
id2 (pr1 a0) ‚ãÜ id2 (pr2 a0) = id2 (pr1 a0 ¬∑ pr2 a0)

id2 f1 ‚ãÜ id2 f2 = id2 (f1 ¬∑ f2)
 apply hcomp_identity.
  
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
‚àè (a0 b0 c0 : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
(f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) a0 b0)
(g : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) b0 c0),
(pr1 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g) ‚ãÜ (pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr2 g) =
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g ‚ãÜ pr2 g
 
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
‚àè
(f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) (f1,, f2) (g1,, g2))
(g : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (hom_ob_mor b c) (g1,, g2) (h1,, h2)),
(pr1 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g) ‚ãÜ (pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr2 g) =
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g ‚ãÜ pr2 g

    
C: bicat
a, b, c: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß

h1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
h2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
‚àè
(f : hom_ob_mor a b ‚ü¶ pr1 (f1,, f2), pr1 (g1,, g2) ‚üß
     √ó hom_ob_mor b c ‚ü¶ pr2 (f1,, f2), pr2 (g1,, g2) ‚üß)
(g : hom_ob_mor a b ‚ü¶ pr1 (g1,, g2), pr1 (h1,, h2) ‚üß
     √ó hom_ob_mor b c ‚ü¶ pr2 (g1,, g2), pr2 (h1,, h2) ‚üß),

(pr1 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g) ‚ãÜ (pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr2 g) =
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr2 f ‚Ä¢ pr1 g ‚ãÜ pr2 g

    
C: bicat
a, b, c: C

f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß

x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2

(pr1 (x1,, x2) ‚Ä¢ pr1 (y1,, y2))
‚ãÜ (pr2 (x1,, x2) ‚Ä¢ pr2 (y1,, y2)) = x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚Ä¢ y1 ‚ãÜ y2
 
C: bicat

x2: f2 ==> g2
y1: g1 ==> h1
y2: g2 ==> h2
(x1 ‚Ä¢ y1) ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚Ä¢ y2) = x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚Ä¢ y1 ‚ãÜ y2
 apply hcomp_vcomp.
Qed.

  : category_binproduct
      (hom a b) (hom b c)
    ‚ü∂

  := make_functor hcomp_functor_data is_functor_hcomp.

is_z_isomorphism
  (lassociator f g h
   :
   hom_precategory a d ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h), f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h ‚üß)

Defined.

a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
rassociator f g h ¬∑ lassociator f g h =
identity (f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h)
C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
lassociator f g h ¬∑ rassociator f g h =
identity (f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h))

  
C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
rassociator f g h ¬∑ lassociator f g h =
identity (f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h)
 apply rassociator_lassociator.
  
C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
lassociator f g h ¬∑ rassociator f g h =
identity (f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h))
 apply lassociator_rassociator.
Defined.


C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
is_iso
  (rassociator f g h
   :
   hom_precategory a d ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h, f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h) ‚üß)


C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
is_iso
  (rassociator f g h
   :
   hom_precategory a d ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ g ¬∑ h, f ¬∑ (g ¬∑ h) ‚üß)

  
C: prebicat
a, b, c, d: C
f: hom_precategory a b
g: hom_precategory b c
h: hom_precategory c d
is_z_isomorphism (rassociator f g h)

  apply is_z_iso_rassociator.
Defined.


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism
  (lunitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ identity a ¬∑ f, f ‚üß)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism
  (lunitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ identity a ¬∑ f, f ‚üß)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_inverse_in_precat (lunitor f) (linvunitor f)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
lunitor f ¬∑ linvunitor f = identity (identity a ¬∑ f)
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
linvunitor f ¬∑ lunitor f = identity f

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
lunitor f ¬∑ linvunitor f = identity (identity a ¬∑ f)
 apply lunitor_linvunitor.
  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
linvunitor f ¬∑ lunitor f = identity f
 apply linvunitor_lunitor.
Defined.


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_iso
  (lunitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ identity a ¬∑ f, f ‚üß)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_iso
  (lunitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ identity a ¬∑ f, f ‚üß)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism (lunitor f)

  apply is_z_iso_lunitor.
Defined.


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism
  (runitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ identity b, f ‚üß)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism
  (runitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ identity b, f ‚üß)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_inverse_in_precat (runitor f) (rinvunitor f)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
runitor f ¬∑ rinvunitor f = identity (f ¬∑ identity b)
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
rinvunitor f ¬∑ runitor f = identity f

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
runitor f ¬∑ rinvunitor f = identity (f ¬∑ identity b)
 apply runitor_rinvunitor.
  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
rinvunitor f ¬∑ runitor f = identity f
 apply rinvunitor_runitor.
Defined.


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_iso
  (runitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ identity b, f ‚üß)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_iso
  (runitor f
   :
   hom_precategory a b ‚ü¶ f ¬∑ identity b, f ‚üß)

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f: hom_precategory a b
is_z_isomorphism (runitor f)

  apply is_z_iso_runitor.
Defined.

End Associators_Unitors_Iso.

(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)
(** ** Functor structure on associators and unitors.                                   *)
(* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *)

Section Associators_Unitors_Natural.

Context {C : prebicat}.

(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
(** Left unitor                                                                       *)
(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
id2 (identity a) ‚ãÜ x ‚Ä¢ lunitor g = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
id2 (identity a) ‚ãÜ x ‚Ä¢ lunitor g = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
((id2 (identity a) ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ (identity a ‚óÉ x))
‚Ä¢ lunitor g = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
(id2 (identity a) ‚ñπ f)
‚Ä¢ ((identity a ‚óÉ x) ‚Ä¢ lunitor g) = lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
(id2 (identity a) ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ (lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x) =
lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
((id2 (identity a) ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ lunitor f) ‚Ä¢ x =
lunitor f ‚Ä¢ x
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
(id2 (identity a) ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ lunitor f = lunitor f

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
id2 (identity a ¬∑ f) ‚Ä¢ lunitor f = lunitor f
 apply id2_left.
Qed.

(*

Definition lunitor_transf (a b : C)
  : bindelta_pair_functor
      (constant_functor (hom_precategory a b) (hom_precategory a a) (identity a))
      (functor_identity (hom_precategory a b)) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    functor_identity (hom_precategory a b)
  := lunitor,, lunitor_natural a b.

(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
(** Right unitor                                                                      *)
(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
x ‚ãÜ id2 (identity b) ‚Ä¢ runitor g = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x


C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
x ‚ãÜ id2 (identity b) ‚Ä¢ runitor g = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
hcomp' x (id2 (identity b)) ‚Ä¢ runitor g =
runitor f ‚Ä¢ x
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
((f ‚óÉ id2 (identity b)) ‚Ä¢ (x ‚ñπ identity b))
‚Ä¢ runitor g = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat

(f ‚óÉ id2 (identity b))
‚Ä¢ ((x ‚ñπ identity b) ‚Ä¢ runitor g) = runitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
(f ‚óÉ id2 (identity b)) ‚Ä¢ (runitor f ‚Ä¢ x) =
runitor f ‚Ä¢ x

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
((f ‚óÉ id2 (identity b)) ‚Ä¢ runitor f) ‚Ä¢ x =
runitor f ‚Ä¢ x
 
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
(f ‚óÉ id2 (identity b)) ‚Ä¢ runitor f = runitor f

  
C: prebicat
a, b: C
f, g: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
x: f ==> g
id2 (f ¬∑ identity b) ‚Ä¢ runitor f = runitor f
 apply id2_left.
Qed.

(*
Definition runitor_transf (a b : C)
  : bindelta_pair_functor
       (functor_identity (hom_precategory a b))
       (constant_functor (hom_precategory a b) (hom_precategory b b) (identity b)) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    functor_identity (hom_precategory a b).
Proof.
  exists runitor. red. apply runitor_natural.
Defined.

(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
(** Left associator.                                                                  *)
(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)

Definition lassociator_fun {a b c d : C}
           (x : C‚ü¶a,b‚üß √ó C‚ü¶b,c‚üß √ó C‚ü¶c,d‚üß)
  :  pr1 x ¬∑ (pr12 x ¬∑ pr22 x) ==> (pr1 x ¬∑ pr12 x) ¬∑ pr22 x
  := lassociator (pr1 x) (pr12 x) (pr22 x).

(*
Lemma lassociator_fun_natural {a b c d : C}
  : is_nat_trans
      (pair_functor (functor_identity (hom_precategory a b)) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor)
      (precategory_binproduct_assoc
         (hom_precategory a b)
         (hom_precategory b c)
         (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
       pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
       hcomp_functor)
      lassociator_fun.
Proof.
  red; cbn. intros (f1, (f2, f3)) (g1, (g2, g3)).
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  intros (x1, (x2, x3)). cbn.
  unfold lassociator_fun. cbn.
  apply hcomp_lassoc.
Qed.

Definition lassociator_transf (a b c d : C)
  : pair_functor (functor_identity (hom_precategory a b)) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    precategory_binproduct_assoc
      (hom_precategory a b)
      (hom_precategory b c)
      (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
  := lassociator_fun,, lassociator_fun_natural.
 *)
(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
(** Right associator.                                                                 *)
(* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------*)

Definition rassociator_fun {a b c d : C}
           (x : C‚ü¶a,b‚üß √ó C‚ü¶b,c‚üß √ó C‚ü¶c,d‚üß)
  : (pr1 x ¬∑ pr12 x) ¬∑ pr22 x ==> pr1 x ¬∑ (pr12 x ¬∑ pr22 x)
  := rassociator (pr1 x) (pr12 x) (pr22 x).

(*
Lemma rassociator_fun_natural {a b c d : C}
  : is_nat_trans
      (precategory_binproduct_assoc
         (hom_precategory a b)
         (hom_precategory b c)
         (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
       pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
       hcomp_functor)
      (pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor)
      rassociator_fun.
Proof.
  red; cbn. intros (f1, (f2, f3)) (g1, (g2, g3)).
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  intros (x1, (x2, x3)). cbn.
  unfold rassociator_fun. cbn.
  apply hcomp_rassoc.
Qed.

Definition rassociator_transf (a b c d : C)
  : precategory_binproduct_assoc
      (hom_precategory a b)
      (hom_precategory b c)
      (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
  := rassociator_fun,, rassociator_fun_natural.
 *)

Definition rassociator_fun' {a b c d : C}
           (x : (C‚ü¶a,b‚üß √ó C‚ü¶b,c‚üß) √ó C‚ü¶c,d‚üß)
  : (pr11 x ¬∑ pr21 x) ¬∑ pr2 x ==> pr11 x ¬∑ (pr21 x ¬∑ pr2 x)
  := rassociator (pr11 x) (pr21 x) (pr2 x).

(*
Lemma rassociator_fun'_natural {a b c d : C}
  : is_nat_trans
      (pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
      (precategory_binproduct_unassoc
         (hom_precategory a b)
         (hom_precategory b c)
         (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
       pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor)
      rassociator_fun'.
Proof.
  red; cbn. intros ((f1, f2), f3) ((g1, g2), g3).
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  unfold precategory_binproduct_mor, hom_ob_mor. cbn.
  intros ((x1, x2), x3). cbn.
  unfold rassociator_fun. cbn.
  apply hcomp_rassoc.
Qed.

Definition rassociator_transf' (a b c d : C)
  : pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    precategory_binproduct_unassoc
      (hom_precategory a b)
      (hom_precategory b c)
      (hom_precategory c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
  := rassociator_fun',, rassociator_fun'_natural.
 *)
End Associators_Unitors_Natural.

Section Associators_Unitors_Natural_bicat.

  Context {C : bicat}.

  Definition lunitor_transf (a b : C)
  : bindelta_pair_functor
      (constant_functor (hom a b) (hom a a) (identity a))
      (functor_identity (hom a b)) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    functor_identity (hom a b)
  := lunitor,, lunitor_natural a b.

  
C: bicat
a, b: C
bindelta_pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
  (constant_functor (hom a b) (hom b b) (identity b))
‚àô hcomp_functor ‚üπ functor_identity (hom a b)


C: bicat
a, b: C
bindelta_pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
  (constant_functor (hom a b) (hom b b) (identity b))
‚àô hcomp_functor ‚üπ functor_identity (hom a b)

  
C: bicat
a, b: C
is_nat_trans
  (bindelta_pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     (constant_functor (hom a b) (hom b b)
        (identity b)) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  (functor_identity (hom a b)) runitor
 
C: bicat
a, b: C
‚àè (x x' : hom a b) (f : hom a b ‚ü¶ x, x' ‚üß),
# (bindelta_pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     (constant_functor (hom a b) (hom b b)
        (identity b)) ‚àô hcomp_functor) f ¬∑ runitor x' =
runitor x ¬∑ # (functor_identity (hom a b)) f
 apply runitor_natural.
Defined.


C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
is_nat_trans
  (pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  ((precategory_binproduct_assoc (hom a b) (hom b c)
      (hom c d)
    ‚àô pair_functor hcomp_functor
        (functor_identity (hom c d))) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  lassociator_fun


C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
is_nat_trans
  (pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  ((precategory_binproduct_assoc (hom a b) (hom b c)
      (hom c d)
    ‚àô pair_functor hcomp_functor
        (functor_identity (hom c d))) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  lassociator_fun

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
‚àè (x x' : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
(f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (precategory_binproduct_ob_mor (hom_ob_mor b c)
          (hom_ob_mor c d)) x x'),
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f) ‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun x' =
lassociator_fun x ‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè
f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
      (precategory_binproduct_ob_mor (hom_ob_mor b c)
         (hom_ob_mor c d)) (f1,, f2,, f3)
      (g1,, g2,, g3),
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè
f : make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß)
      (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß, f ==> g)
    ‚ü¶ pr1 (f1,, f2,, f3), pr1 (g1,, g2,, g3) ‚üß
    √ó precategory_binproduct_ob_mor
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß, f ==> g))
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß, f ==> g))
      ‚ü¶ pr2 (f1,, f2,, f3), pr2 (g1,, g2,, g3) ‚üß,
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè
f : f1 ==> g1
    √ó precategory_binproduct_mor
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß, f ==> g))
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß, f ==> g)) (f2,, f3)
        (g2,, g3),
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè
f : f1 ==> g1
    √ó make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
        (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß, f ==> g) ‚ü¶ pr1 (f2,, f3),
      pr1 (g2,, g3) ‚üß
      √ó make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
          (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß, f ==> g)
        ‚ü¶ pr2 (f2,, f3), pr2 (g2,, g3) ‚üß,
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè f : f1 ==> g1 √ó f2 ==> g2 √ó f3 ==> g3,
pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
x3: f3 ==> g3
pr1 (x1,, x2,, x3)
‚ãÜ (pr12 (x1,, x2,, x3) ‚ãÜ pr22 (x1,, x2,, x3))
‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 (x1,, x2,, x3) ‚ãÜ pr12 (x1,, x2,, x3)
  ‚ãÜ pr22 (x1,, x2,, x3)
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
x3: f3 ==> g3
x1 ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚ãÜ x3) ‚Ä¢ lassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
lassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3) ‚Ä¢ x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚ãÜ x3

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
x3: f3 ==> g3
x1 ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚ãÜ x3)
‚Ä¢ lassociator (pr1 (g1,, g2,, g3))
    (pr12 (g1,, g2,, g3)) (pr22 (g1,, g2,, g3)) =
lassociator (pr1 (f1,, f2,, f3)) (pr12 (f1,, f2,, f3))
  (pr22 (f1,, f2,, f3)) ‚Ä¢ x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚ãÜ x3
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
x1: f1 ==> g1
x2: f2 ==> g2
x3: f3 ==> g3
x1 ‚ãÜ (x2 ‚ãÜ x3) ‚Ä¢ lassociator g1 g2 g3 =
lassociator f1 f2 f3 ‚Ä¢ x1 ‚ãÜ x2 ‚ãÜ x3

  apply hcomp_lassoc.
Qed.

Definition lassociator_transf (a b c d : C)
  : pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b)) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    precategory_binproduct_assoc
      (hom a b)
      (hom b c)
      (hom c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
  := lassociator_fun,, lassociator_fun_natural.

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
is_nat_trans
  ((precategory_binproduct_assoc (hom a b) (hom b c)
      (hom c d)
    ‚àô pair_functor hcomp_functor
        (functor_identity (hom c d))) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  (pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor) rassociator_fun


C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
is_nat_trans
  ((precategory_binproduct_assoc (hom a b) (hom b c)
      (hom c d)
    ‚àô pair_functor hcomp_functor
        (functor_identity (hom c d))) ‚àô hcomp_functor)
  (pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
     hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor) rassociator_fun

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
‚àè (x x' : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß √ó C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
(f : precategory_binproduct_mor (hom_ob_mor a b)
       (precategory_binproduct_ob_mor (hom_ob_mor b c)
          (hom_ob_mor c d)) x x'),
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f ‚Ä¢ rassociator_fun x' =
rassociator_fun x ‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
 
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
f3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè

      (precategory_binproduct_ob_mor (hom_ob_mor b c)
         (hom_ob_mor c d)) (f1,, f2,, f3)
      (g1,, g2,, g3),
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f
‚Ä¢ rassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
rassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)

  
C: bicat
a, b, c, d: C
f1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
f2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß

g1: C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß
g2: C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß
g3: C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß
‚àè
f : make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß)
      (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ a, b ‚üß, f ==> g)
    ‚ü¶ pr1 (f1,, f2,, f3), pr1 (g1,, g2,, g3) ‚üß
    √ó precategory_binproduct_ob_mor
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß, f ==> g))
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß)
           (Œª f g : C ‚ü¶ c, d ‚üß, f ==> g))
      ‚ü¶ pr2 (f1,, f2,, f3), pr2 (g1,, g2,, g3) ‚üß,
pr1 f ‚ãÜ pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f
‚Ä¢ rassociator_fun (g1,, g2,, g3) =
rassociator_fun (f1,, f2,, f3)
‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)
 
C: bicat

‚àè

    √ó precategory_binproduct_mor
        (make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)

‚Ä¢ pr1 f ‚ãÜ (pr12 f ‚ãÜ pr22 f)

‚àè

    √ó make_precategory_ob_mor (C ‚ü¶ b, c ‚üß)

  apply hcomp_rassoc.

Definition rassociator_transf (a b c d : C)
  : precategory_binproduct_assoc
      (hom a b)
      (hom b c)
      (hom c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
  := rassociator_fun,, rassociator_fun_natural.


C: bicat

is_nat_trans
  (pair_functor hcomp_functor
     (functor_identity (hom c d)) ‚àô hcomp_functor)

      (hom c d)
    ‚àô pair_functor (functor_identity (hom a b))
        hcomp_functor) ‚àô hcomp_functor)

Definition rassociator_transf' (a b c d : C)
  : pair_functor hcomp_functor (functor_identity _) ‚àô
    hcomp_functor
    ‚üπ
    precategory_binproduct_unassoc
      (hom a b)
      (hom b c)
      (hom c d) ‚àô
    pair_functor (functor_identity _) hcomp_functor ‚àô hcomp_functor
  := rassociator_fun',, rassociator_fun'_natural.

End Associators_Unitors_Natural_bicat.

functor_data (hom b z) (hom a z)

‚àè a0 b0 : hom b z,

B: bicat
